### 1. User and Role Management

### API 1 User Registration
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",
    "password":"premkumar45",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}




### API 2 User Register Missing Name 
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",
    "password":"premkumar45",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}


### API 3 User Register Missing Email
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",   
    "password":"premkumar45",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}


### API 4 User Register Missing Password
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",   
    "role":"ADMIN"
