### API 6 User Register Invalid Role 
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",
    "password":"premkumar45",
    "role":"INVALIDROLE"
}




### API 7 User Register Weak Password 
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",
    "password":"week",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}



### API 8 User Register Invalid Email Format 
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45ssscasgjfd",
    "password":"premkakkkssk",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}




### API 9 User Register User (Duplicate Email)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/register
Content-Type:application/json

{
        "name":"Prem Kumar",
    "email":"premkumarjp45@gmail.com",
    "password":"premkumar45",
    "role":"ADMIN"
}





